{"word":"G4100 - πιστεύω - pisteúō - pist-yoo'-o - Believe","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πιστεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>pisteúō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pist-yoo'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Believe"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"நம்புதல் - வினைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to believe"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4102 - πίστις - pístis - pis'-tis/4102\">G4102</a>; to <i>have faith</i> (in, upon, or with respect to, a person or thing), that is, <i>credit</i>; by implication to <i>entrust</i> (especially one&rsquo;s spiritual well being to Christ): - believe (-r), commit (to trust), put in trust with."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3640 - ὀλιγόπιστος - oligópistos - ol-ig-op'-is-tos/3640\">G3640</a>, <a href=\"#/G4100 - πιστεύω - pisteúō - pist-yoo'-o/4100\">G4100</a>, <a href=\"#/G4102 - πίστις - pístis - pis'-tis/4102\">G4102</a>, <a href=\"#/G4103 - πιστός - pistós - pis-tos'/4103\">G4103</a>, <a href=\"#/G4104 - πιστόω - pistóō - pis-to'-o/4104\">G4104</a>, <a href=\"#/G569 - ἀπιστέω - apistéō - ap-is-teh'-o/569\">G569</a>, <a href=\"#/G570 - ἀπιστία - apistía - ap-is-tee'-ah/570\">G570</a>, <a href=\"#/G571 - ἄπιστος - ápistos - ap'-is-tos/571\">G571</a>"}]}